<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css" />
    <title>Createev</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">
            <a href="/">
                <img src="/main-logo.png" alt="" />
            </a>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul id="MenuItems">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/product">Products</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About us</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact us</a></li>
                <li><a href="/account">Account</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="cart">
                <img src="/shopping-cart.png" alt="" class="cart-icon" />
            </a>
        </nav>
        <img src="/menu.png" alt="" class="menu-icon" id="menu-icon" onclick="menutoggle()" />
    </div>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-2">
                    <h1>Life has many surprises, <br />The little things do too.</h1>
                    <p>
                        What's in a name? That which we call a rose.<br />
                        By any other name would smell as sweet.
                    </p>
                    <a href="product" class="btn">See more &#8594;</a>
                </div>
