                <div class="col-3">
                    <img src="./quote.png" alt="" id="quote-icon" />
                    <p>
                        Hiii I got it na po!!! angganda ganda aaaaa üò≠ sayang lang di ko agad mabibigay sa pagbibigyan ko, I‚Äôll definitely order again from u!!!
                    </p>
                    <img src="./testimonial2.jpg" alt="" id="feedback-img" />
                    <h3>Anthonty To</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col-3">
                    <img src="./quote.png" alt="" id="quote-icon" />
                    <p>
                        The shop has a very accommodating seller and they really made sure that the item you ordered will be delivered ASAP/on time. The items are great to give to your special someone! I highly recommend this shop! üòäüíñ
                    </p>
                    <img src="./testimonial3.jpg" alt="" id="feedback-img" />
